=Review this extraction draft. You CANNOT see the transcript directly — you must call tools.

opportunity_id: {{ $json.opportunity_id }}

draft_payload (extraction agent's proposal):
{{ JSON.stringify($json.draft_payload) }}

reasoning_trace (claims to verify):
{{ JSON.stringify($json.draft_reasoning_trace) }}

evidence_list (pass this to quote_grounding):
{{ JSON.stringify($json.evidence_list) }}

draft_abstain: {{ $json.draft_abstain }}

Call quote_grounding(evidence_list), then schema_validator(candidate_payload=draft_payload, abstain_mode=draft_abstain), then uncertainty_check(draft_payload). Then emit verdict.

